overview: Excelacom is a leading Software and Consulting company, providing strategy and support for leading companies across four continents. Excelacom’s mission is to enhance the businesses of our clients through innovations in business process architecture, application strategy, and IT infrastructure. This mission is supported by more than 600 consultants, analysts and technology specialists in 6 offices worldwide. Excelacom produces a specialized line of telecommunications products under the Century brand and provides consulting, system integration and outsourcing services.
